<template>
    <b-form-group
                :id="'input-' + inputName"
                :label="labelText"
                :label-for="'input-'+ inputName"
            >
            <b-form-input
                :id="'input-' + inputName"
                v-model="value"
                @keyup="$emit('updateField', value)"
                :type="type"
                required
                :placeholder="placeholder"
             ></b-form-input>
    </b-form-group>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data(){
        return {
            value
        }
    },
    props:  [
        'labelText',
        'inputName',
        'placeholder',
        'type'
    ]
}
</script>
